name: BaddestBltchWalk
description:
A small single-level game for a game jam.👻
  • Trying to mimic R2Beat but so hard to match level obstacles with music tempo, so instead of a complex level that fails on most keystrokes,  the level is really simple and straightforward.😥
  • Also inspired by Aggretsuko, Washami Gori walk is so addictive.😆
  • No offense on the game title, it's the  name of the music when I found it on youtube 🥺
  • Sorry Washami fans for the ugly model, just started learning blender for 20 hrs.. 😂
  • I love Haida 🥵
